        <detaileddescription>
<para>Dumps out a list of I3C messages. For any that are writes (W), the data is displayed in hex.</para>
<para>It looks something like this (with name &quot;testing&quot;):</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">D:<sp/>I3C<sp/>msg:<sp/>testing,<sp/>addr=56</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">D:<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>W<sp/>len=01:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">D:<sp/>contents:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">D:<sp/>06<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>|.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">D:<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>W<sp/>len=0e:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">D:<sp/>contents:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">D:<sp/>00<sp/>01<sp/>02<sp/>03<sp/>04<sp/>05<sp/>06<sp/>07<sp/>|........</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">D:<sp/>08<sp/>09<sp/>0a<sp/>0b<sp/>0c<sp/>0d<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>|......</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
